trans-unit.source: A helper class that creates <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence"></xref> instances.

Once created, the DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator creates new <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence> instances, sets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.InstanceId%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.SequenceId%2A> and increments the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.MessageNumber%2A> for each successive <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence> instance created.
trans-unit.target: Når opprettet av DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator oppretter ny <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence>forekomster, angir den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.InstanceId%2A>, <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.SequenceId%2A>og øker den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.MessageNumber%2A>for hvert etterfølgende <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence>forekomst som er opprettet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.MessageNumber%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.SequenceId%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence.InstanceId%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequence>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator"></xref> class with the specified instance ID and sequence ID.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.DiscoveryMessageSequenceGenerator"> </xref> klasse med angitt forekomst-ID og sequence-ID.
